Dear {!Primary_Applicant_Name__c},

Greetings from Runwal Enterprises!!

We are pleased to inform you that your agreement document is now ready for collection. Please find the details below for your reference:

Project: {!Project__r.Name}
Tower/Wing: {!Tower__r.Name}
Unit Number: {!Unit_No__r.Name}
Agreement Number: {{Agreement_Number}}

You may kindly visit the site office at your convenience to collect the agreement document.

If you require any assistance or would like to schedule a visit, please feel free to contact your Relationship Manager or the site office.

Thank you for choosing Runwal Enterprises.

Warm regards,
Runwal Enterprises
